name: Spinarak
flavorText:
It lies still in
the same pose for
days in its web, waiting for its
unsuspecting prey
to wander close.

previous.name: Ledian
previous.flavorText:
When the stars
flicker in the
night sky, it flutters about,
scattering a
glowing powder.

next.name: Ariados
next.flavorText:
It spins string
not only from its
rear but also from its mouth. It is
hard to tell which
end is which.
